-# ID
- id = 0

%p
    JavaScript is required for the navigation collapse
    Be sure to add a role="navigation" to the navbar to help with accessibility.

    Requires a /data/navigation.yaml file to be present. Basically checks the
    YAML for Divider, Dropdown or Menu Item then displays according to the YAML.

-# Set globally want per nav bar....
- dataNav[ :container ] = "container"

-# Default
:ruby
    code = %{partial "./molecule/navbar/navbar", locals: dataNav}

-# Code
= partial "./organism/code/code", locals: { id: id += 1, code: code, heading: { text: "Default" } }

